<h2 style='font-style: normal;font-weight: 700;Margin-bottom: 0;Margin-top: 0;font-size: 24px;line-height: 32px;font-family: "Lato",sans-serif;color: #44a8c7;text-align: left;'><span style="color:#2a96ff">Tilbakestilling av Plendit-passord</span></h2>

<p style='font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;Margin-bottom: 10px;Margin-top: 16px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 24px;font-family: "Lato",sans-serif;color: #60666d;text-align: left;'>
    Hei <%= @resource.email %>.
</p>

<p style='font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;Margin-bottom: 10px;Margin-top: 16px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 24px;font-family: "Lato",sans-serif;color: #60666d;text-align: left;'>
    Noen har bedt om en lenke for å endre passordet for Plendit.no -  Bruk lenken under for å:
    <%= link_to 'Endre passord', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %>
</p>

<p>
    Hvis du ikke har bedt om å endre passordet ditt, kan du ignorere denne e-posten.
</p>
